00:31:33.050 --> 00:31:37.280
Those are then things that
young people can do and can

00:31:37.280 --> 00:31:39.360
motivate their parents to do.

00:31:39.360 --> 00:31:41.490
All of that, then,
is the background

00:31:41.490 --> 00:31:47.910
to my pleasure at seeing a young
people's edition of my book

00:31:47.910 --> 00:31:51.200
"The Third Chimpanzee"
