agriculture has created.

00:32:54.450 --> 00:32:55.910
JARED DIAMOND: Yeah.

00:32:55.910 --> 00:33:00.010
When one looks at the
problems of the world,

00:33:00.010 --> 00:33:04.720
certainly I go back and
forth between being depressed

00:33:04.720 --> 00:33:08.350
and being optimistic, or
being cautiously optimistic,

00:33:08.350 --> 00:33:10.060
or being very optimistic.

00:33:10.060 --> 00:33:14.720
When I wrote that essay, I
was in a pessimistic mood.

00:33:14.720 --> 00:33:18.470
In the last several years--
so in the last several years

00:33:18.470 --> 00:33:20.817
there are more and
more people exercising

00:33:20.817 --> 00:33:22.150
more and more destructive power.

00:33:22.150 --> 00:33:25.290
But there have also been some
developments for the good

00:33:25.290 --> 00:33:26.770
in the last several years.

00:33:26.770 --> 00:33:28.610
Three years ago most
Americans did not

00:33:28.610 --> 00:33:31.220
