00:34:12.409 --> 00:34:18.449
So that's why the chair of the
board of World Wildlife Fund

00:34:18.449 --> 00:34:21.230
now is the former
CEO of Coca-Cola.

00:34:21.230 --> 00:34:23.409
In short, in response
to your question,

00:34:23.409 --> 00:34:27.449
I wrote that essay at a
time when I felt pessimistic

00:34:27.449 --> 00:34:30.770
and there will I'm sure be
