JARED DIAMOND: Yes?

00:34:42.190 --> 00:34:44.600
AUDIENCE: So thank you
for your introduction

00:34:44.600 --> 00:34:46.704
on why you wrote this book.

00:34:46.704 --> 00:34:49.480
So I wonder about the
2% difference in genome.

00:34:49.480 --> 00:34:52.969
Could you show examples
